   "title": "Abandonment Program (rev3.0)",
   "steps": [
    "MIRU service rig and associated equipment.",
    "NU Class II 2M BOPE c/w Class A monitoring system on 8-5/8\" casing. Call for CalGEM inspection. (Assumed BHP ~1,293 psi; normally pressured at 0.43 psi/ft — top perf 3,443 ft MD = 3,007 ft TVD.)",
